，还会感到尴尬、放不开。 好在妻子很支持他，理解他所做的一切。小陈表示，自己现在还在备考，同时也在自学剪辑，记录着摆摊的趣事。90后老师失业到校门口卖火鸡面：开始放不开，遇家长会尴尬"},"attached_info":"CkEI3pLImqL4xP9hEAMaCTExMzk2Mzk2MCCIkM6+BjAAOGRADnILMTQ5MTE1MDg0Njl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"124 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-a1b56f33459e7d4010dfad6a2841658b_1440w.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"15_1742387316.113461","card_id":"Q_15202571234","card_label":{"type":"new","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":15202571234,"title":"如何看待 2025 年湖北省七市州高三联考语文试卷疑似出现命题组原创「唐诗」，这是否合适？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/15202571234","type":"question","created":1742206108,"answer_count":22,"follower_count":54,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[2726,5758,5830,15223,80811],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"如题，此次考试考察了一首名为《秋江别友》的“唐诗”，作者为王晦之，并要求学生进行赏析，然而事后有人发现这首诗疑似为命题组原创，在网络上无法搜索到其出处，这是否合适？ https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzUyNzE3MTA4MQ==&mid=2247677584&idx=8&sn=3ba1b4018c7d1cd9b3b01c2372fe5877&chksm=fbabad0c2fa6b779c05774a1a4d6e4ecb6a763cba0b52cd0bbedbd2982e3826b455153fab0a6&scene=27"},"attached_info":"CkEI3pLImqL4xP9hEAMaCTExNDAyNTM1MiCc6d++BjAAODZAD3ILMTUyMDI1NzEyMzR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"116 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-e42446423cc49f2e69fead8028bf6065_1440w.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"16_1742387316.114405","card_id":"Q_15000572929","target":{"id":15000572929,"title":"老板说年轻人别太看重工资，要看成长机会，这是洗脑神技还是人生真理？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/15000572929","type":"question","created":1742002277,"answer_count":354,"follower_count":473,"author":{"type":